Package com.twitter.common.thrift.callers

Interface Summary
Caller A caller that invokes a method on an object.
Caller.ResultCapture Captures the result of a request, whether synchronous or asynchronous.
 

Class Summary
Caller.WrappedMethodCallback A callback that adapts a Caller.ResultCapture with an AsyncMethodCallback while maintaining the AsyncMethodCallback interface.
DeadlineCaller A caller that imposes a time deadline on the underlying caller.
DebugCaller A caller that reports debugging information about calls.
RetryingCaller A caller that will retry calls to the wrapped caller.
StatTrackingCaller A caller that exports statistics about calls made to the wrapped caller.
ThriftCaller<T> A caller that issues calls to a target that is assumed to be a client to a thrift service.
